Navigate to CloudFormation  Select the CloudFormation Service.    Confirm you are in the eu-west-1 (Ireland) region.
 Create a new CloudFormation Stack  Select &lsquo;Create Stack&rsquo;    Note that the Factory Initialization Stack has been deployed. If yours has not refer to &lsquo;Install Factory Process&rsquo;
 Select the pre-configured CloudFormation Template Service Catalog Puppet can be installed via a pre-created CloudFormation Template stored in S3 under the following URL: &gt; https://service-catalog-tools.
